Package: ilog
Title: Intelligent logarithms
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Jarad", "Niemi", email = "niemi@iastate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Intelligently take logarithms of values that are possibly zero.
    Defaults to adding the minimum non-zero value before taking the logarithm.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Suggests:
    testthat
